\section desc Description
Classes defining the Particle Data Table Event Setup Source.

\subsection interface Public interface
None.<br><br>
An example of how to configure a job to use the Particle Data Table Event Setup Source
is presented below:
\htmlonly
<pre>
  es_source = HepPDTESSource {
    string pdtFileName = "/afs/cern.ch/.../PDG_mass_width_2004.mc"
  }
</pre>
\endhtmlonly

\subsection modules Modules
None.

\subsection tests Unit tests and examples
- <b>testPDT.cfg</b>: example of how to retrieve PDT from the Event Setup using
the Event Setup Source.

